name: garden-analytics-script
description: Analytics script for tracking traffic and wallet data

scripts.obfuscate: javascript-obfuscator script.js --output script.obf.js --compact true --domain-lock ["http://localhost:5173","https://beta.garden.finance","https://new.garden.finance"] --domain-lock-redirect-url https://new.garden.finance --string-array-encoding rc4 --string-array-threshold 1 --transform-object-keys true --target browser --identifier-names-generator hexadecimal --rename-globals true --dead-code-injection-threshold 1
scripts.git_force_push: git add . && git commit --no-edit --amend && git push origin main --force
